gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Wizards 110, Nets 104
gameRecap.excerpt: The Wizards defeated the Nets, 110-104. Kyle Kuzma led the way for the Wizards with 26 points, eight rebounds, and four 3PM, while Deni Avdija added 21 points, 13 rebounds, and six assists in the victory. Mikal Bridges tallied 19 points and five rebounds for the Nets in the losing effort. The Wizards improve to 6-25 on the season, while the Nets fall to 15-17.
